show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/k7UfTy
show.description: Aditya Deshpandey  is a wealthy yet lonely businessman, and Roohi is a self-made woman who runs a food stall, battling the scars of broken relationships, a cruel daughter-in-law, and past humiliations. Their paths cross through Aditya’s daughter, Taanvi where a simple matchmaking attempt turns into a profound tale. Aditya hides his true identity, wanting to see if Roohi loves him or merely his wealth. But for Roohi, this relationship goes far beyond love — during this journey, she finds the daughter she lost five years ago.
